### 1. Create a new task
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Solve DSA question",
  "description": "Solved 2 questions from CodeWithMik",
  "status": "completed",
  "day": "2025-09-20",
  "timeSpent": 60
}

### 2. Create another task
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cohort Study",
  "description": "Watched TakeUForward recursion video",
  "status": "in-progress",
  "day": "2025-09-20",
