---

### 3. Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks

### 4. Get tasks for a specific day
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks?day=2025-09-20

### 5. Get tasks in a date range
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks?start=2025-09-15&end=2025-09-20

---

